  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/a0fd42f4b79305e30e932301b24116ad.poster.avif?t=1765727368\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/a0fd42f4b79305e30e932301b24116ad.webm?t=1765727368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/a0fd42f4b79305e30e932301b24116ad.mp4?t=1765727368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/be07aebd9e3530261283fed8c281d1dc.webp?t=1765727368\" width=26 height=16 /></span> In Time Handlers, dive into an exhilarating cooperative adventure with a friend. Become employees of the mysterious Time Company tasked with repairing the spatio-temporal rifts that threaten the balance of time and space that manifest across different eras. Face bewildering and exciting challenges.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/e7047f30fdaa80ded31a1dd3149ec679.poster.avif?t=1765727368\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/e7047f30fdaa80ded31a1dd3149ec679.webm?t=1765727368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/e7047f30fdaa80ded31a1dd3149ec679.mp4?t=1765727368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/be07aebd9e3530261283fed8c281d1dc.webp?t=1765727368\" width=26 height=16 /></span> In this 3D puzzle game, you explore a mysterious tower filled with challenging obstacles. Each floor presents new complex puzzles that require close communication and flawless cooperation between the two players. Be creative, solve twisted riddles, and use your wits to progress.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/4f0485840c8cfc8d27eb6d15de77e722.poster.avif?t=1765727368\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/4f0485840c8cfc8d27eb6d15de77e722.webm?t=1765727368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/4f0485840c8cfc8d27eb6d15de77e722.mp4?t=1765727368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/be07aebd9e3530261283fed8c281d1dc.webp?t=1765727368\" width=26 height=16 /></span> The narrator will follow your progress in the tower, so be prepared for sharp comments and witty remarks that spice up your interactions with the game.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/fe46dc0859b131148a849f60d6a2c1da.poster.avif?t=1765727368\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/fe46dc0859b131148a849f60d6a2c1da.webm?t=1765727368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/fe46dc0859b131148a849f60d6a2c1da.mp4?t=1765727368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/be07aebd9e3530261283fed8c281d1dc.webp?t=1765727368\" width=26 height=16 /></span> Your ultimate goal is to climb the tower's floors, solve all the complex puzzles, and reach the heart of the spatio-temporal rift. Only skillful puzzle-solving will allow you to restore order in the universe and mend the tears of time.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/d19296445dd772251a66556fa81cbd40.poster.avif?t=1765727368\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/d19296445dd772251a66556fa81cbd40.webm?t=1765727368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/d19296445dd772251a66556fa81cbd40.mp4?t=1765727368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/be07aebd9e3530261283fed8c281d1dc.webp?t=1765727368\" width=26 height=16 /></span> Will you succeed in solving puzzles to repair the rift that threatens time?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/be07aebd9e3530261283fed8c281d1dc.webp?t=1765727368\" width=26 height=16 /></span> What are these rifts really?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448830/extras/be07aebd9e3530261283fed8c281d1dc.webp?t=1765727368\" width=26 height=16 /></span> What is the narrator's purpose and who is he?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Answer these questions through the different trials you will encounter!</h2>",
